release.body:
<!-- Release notes generated using configuration in .github/release.yml at 4.0.x -->

## What's Changed
### Breaking Changes 🛠
* Change annotation-based CORS to match configuration-based defaults by @wetted in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9509
### Bug Fixes 🐞
* KSP: Properly map suspended function class by @dstepanov in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9520
* use binary name to store annotation names in metadata for KSP by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9536
* Fixed incorrect ability to disable slf4j by @altro3 in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9532
* Fix KSP nullability handling by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9538
* fix: txt/plain possible for BigDecimal by @sdelamo in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9535

### Dependency updates 🚀
* Update dependency io.micronaut.build.internal:micronaut-gradle-plugins to v6.5.1 by @renovate in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9521
* Update dependency io.micronaut.rxjava2:micronaut-rxjava2-bom to v2.0.0-M6 by @renovate in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9488
* Update dependency io.micronaut.groovy:micronaut-runtime-groovy to v4.0.0-M4 by @renovate in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9475
* chore(deps): update dependency io.micronaut.build.internal:micronaut-gradle-plugins to v6.5.3 by @renovate in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9540
* fix(deps): update dependency com.github.javaparser:javaparser-symbol-solver-core to v3.25.4 by @renovate in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9533

### Build 🐘
* core: enable binary compatability check by @wetted in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9505
* Manual sync of graalvm workflows by @msupic in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9539


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/compare/v4.0.0-RC4...v4.0.0-RC5
